# UI Components and Styling

## Component Libraries

### shadcn/ui

- Use [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/) for base UI components
- Style: "new-york"
- Components located in `src/components/ui/`
- Current components: Card, Drawer, Select, Separator
- Add new components using: `npx shadcn@latest add [component-name]`

### Custom Components

- Use custom components for complex, feature-specific UI
- Located in `src/components/` and `src/features/*/components/`
- Examples: CommandPalette, NavigationHeader, PostSidebar

## Styling Approach

### Tailwind CSS

- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes for styling
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Use `cn()` utility from `@/utils/misc` for conditional classes
- Import pattern: `import { cn } from "@/utils/misc"`

### CSS Custom Properties

Located in `src/css/*.css`:

- **`globals.css`** - Main stylesheet, imports theme and animations

  - Overrides library & prose defaults
  - Custom scrollbar styles
  - Markdown/prose overrides
  - Selection styles

- **`theme.css`** - Tailwind CSS theme variables

  - Color system (OKLCH color space)
  - Font variables (`--font-firaSans`, `--font-catamaran`)
  - Custom colors (primary-green, secondary-green, etc.)
  - Spacing variables (header, mobile-nav)
  - Animation references

- **`animations.css`** - CSS keyframes

  - `conic-gradient` - Rotating gradient animation
  - `scroll-right` / `scroll-left` - Horizontal scrolling animations
  - Use as Tailwind utilities: `animate-conic-gradient`, `animate-scroll-right`, etc.

- **`shiki.css`** - Syntax highlighting styles
  - Code block styling
  - Line number formatting
  - Highlighted line indicators
  - Uses rehype-pretty-code plugin

## Component Patterns

### Component Structure

```typescript
import * as React from "react";
import { cn } from "@/utils/misc";

function Component({ className, ...props }: React.ComponentProps<"div">) {
  return (
    <div
      data-slot="component-name"
      className={cn("base-classes", className)}
      {...props}
    />
  );
}
```

### Key Patterns

- **`cn()` utility**: Always use for className merging
- **Spread props**: Use `React.ComponentProps<"element">` for type safety
- **Compound components**: Export multiple related components (e.g., Card, CardHeader, CardContent)

### Client Components

- Mark with `"use client"` directive when needed
- Use for interactive components, hooks, or browser APIs

## Design System

### Colors

- Primary: Green (`--color-primary-green: #bfe81c`)
- Secondary: Green (`--color-secondary-green: #b0c84e`)
- Use semantic color tokens: `bg-card`, `text-foreground`, `border-border`, etc.

### Typography

- Headings: Fira Sans (`--font-firaSans`)
- Body: Catamaran (`--font-catamaran`)
- Prose: Use `prose prose-invert` classes for markdown content
  - Ensure `globals.css` styles are used, respected and override `prose` defaults as needed

### Spacing

- Header spacing: `--spacing-header: 55px`
- Mobile nav spacing: `--spacing-mobile-nav: 68px`
- Use Tailwind spacing scale for consistency
- Use consistent spacing throughout the project

## Responsive Design

- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints: `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`
- Use `useMedia` hook for conditional rendering
- Ensure behaviour is consistent across all breakpoints
